==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dirk
<hw>Dirk</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ir.
<ets>duirc</ets>.]</ety> <def>A kind of dagger or poniard; -- formerly
much used by the Scottish Highlander.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Dirk knife</b></col>, <cd>a clasp knife having a large,
dirklike blade.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dirk</ent>⟦br⟧

